# Customer Portal PR Checklist (UI)

Before merging UI work:

## Styling

- [ ] No **new** `*.module.css` or component-scoped `.scss` files
- [ ] Colors use design tokens (`bg-bg-basic`, `text-text-heading`, `border-border-default`, `bg-portal-sidebar-start`, etc.)
- [ ] No new `bg-[#...]` / `text-gray-*` when a token exists
- [ ] Touching a component with a CSS module → migrate module to inline Tailwind in the same PR when feasible (boy scout rule)

## Interactive UI

- [ ] Prefer `@laitram-l-l-c/intralox-ui-components` via `src/components/ui/` wrappers
- [ ] Direct `react-aria-components` only when DS lacks the primitive; follow `ui-components.mdc`
- [ ] Dialogs: controlled `isOpen` on overlay — no `if (!isOpen) return null`
- [ ] Tables: `selectionMode` + `Checkbox slot="selection"` when row selection is enabled

## Metrics (track over time)

| Metric                                | Target                             |
| ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `*.module.css` under `src/components` | Decrease each sprint; goal &lt; 30 |
| TSX files importing `*.module.css`    | Decrease; goal &lt; 15%            |

